1. What is the main reason to include a demo in your presentation?
Solution : A. People learn from a demo because they can see how something is actually done

2. What should you do when demoing technology during a presentation?
Solution : C. If you use a story, try to include characters and situations your primary audience will relate to

3. Which of the following steps are important when preparing your technology for a demo?
Solution : D. Take screenshots of key screens in case something goes wrong and your demo dosen't work
